           Ver. 1.1.0 2026-04-18

 [1mFeature: [0m256-color and true-color
   ANSI support. Parse, render and
   save xterm-256 and 24-bit RGB
   escape sequences.

 [1mFeature: [0m256-color picker popup
   added to the palette sidebar.

 [1mFeature: [0mView > Extended Colors
   toggle (Ctrl+Shift+E). Live
   preview art with extended colors
   on or off before saving.

 [1mFeature: [0mAuto-detect extended
   colors when opening 256 or
   true-color ANSI files.

 [1mFix: [0mAll drawing tools updated
   to paint with extended colors:
   brush, line, rectangle, ellipse,
   fill bucket, shifter & cursor.

 [1mFix: [0mEyedropper captures extended
   colors; toolbar sample preview
   shows true block colors.

 [1mOptimisation: [0mGlyph and background
   canvas caching for instant
   extended color rendering.

