           Ver. 1.0.22 2019-08-29

 [1mFeature[0m: Visual cue between selection and
   operation mode for selections.

 [1mFeature[0m: Scrolling Canvas now works
   anywhere.

 [1mFeature[0m: Insert/Delete Row Insert/
