           Ver. 1.0.21 2019-08-26

 [1mFeature[0m: The vertical block shifter now
   uses the current foreground colour if
   it isn't shifting an existing block.

 [1mFeature[0m: Middle/wheel mouse button zooms
   to actual size.

 [1mFeature[0m: Alt+A is an alias for Select
   Attribute.

 [1mFeature[0m: Retention time for pasting online
   now configurable in preferences.

 [1mFeature[0m: Revert To Last Save.

 [1mFeature[0m: Erase to Start and End of Line.

 [1mFix[0m: Fresh documents now respect
   smallscale guides on by default setting.

 [1mFix[0m: Erase is only called once, and not
   twice.

 [1mFix[0m: Stamping a block will not be mirrored
   if it crosses the midpoint of the
   canvas.

 [1mFix[0m: Pressing M to return to keyboard mode
   no longer registers when used with a
   modifier.

 [1mFix[0m: The guide border is now visible on a
   white background.

 [1mFix[0m: Select Attribute now visible in Menu.

 [1mFix[0m: Selection now works as expected at
   at canvas boundaries.

 [1mFix[0m: Certain menu items with hotkeys now
   work as expected.

 [1mFix[0m: Document dimensions on status bar now
   update as expected on document load.

 [1mFix[0m: Disable Character Palette and
   Dictation menu-items on MacOS.

 [1mFix[0m: Cursor now redraws after undo, redo,
